org.openimaj.audio.util

Class MusicUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.audio.util.MusicUtils

  • public class MusicUtils
extends Object
    Static utility methods that are related to music (more semantic than audio utilities).

    For working with notes, see WesternScaleNote.

    Author:
    David Dupplaw (dpd@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
